name: Cappadocia
description: This photo was taken in 2017 in Cappadocia, Turkey.  The picture was taken on an early morning flight in a hot air balloon in the stunning Cappadocian landscape.  The camera lens captured both the amazing view of Cappadocia and the shadow of the balloon blooming in the mountains, and a detective with a handbag and a hat, who watches what is happening from the side, we will see you find him :)
